}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "P1M-1109000-01G" and "D-HUB4P VR1.3" is silkscreened on the board of the hub used to populate this entry (S/N: ZTS8V200175, addl. model / lot ID 8H18A ???). :The radial capacitors are '''DON''' and '''Su'scon''' branded.
The power adapter included with the device may be an unbranded ''Switching Power Adaptor'' model LK-SA-05-2600-JU + addl. text 234-JU-ROHS-XZF (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 1.0 max. -> 5VDC, 2.6A).
